OL,5,CTrent
OL,7,FA man has been jailed for 11 years
OL,8,Fafter he killed another man in a
OL,9,Fcollision in Stoke-on-Trent.
OL,11,F21-year-old Leon Salt had previously
OL,12,Fadmitted causing the death of 51-year-
OL,13,Fold Christopher Deaville after he
OL,14,Fstruck him with a stolen car in
OL,15,FNewcastle Lane in Penkhull on April
OL,16,F11th.
OL,18,FSalt was driving a black Mini Cooper
OL,19,Fthat had been stolen just a few days
OL,20,Fbefore when he hit Christopher while
OL,21,Fovertaking another car.
