OL,7,FChristopher died at the scene and Salt
OL,8,Fcontinued to drive off.
OL,10,FThe Mini was found just over a mile
OL,11,Faway after it had been dumped in an
OL,12,Falleyway between Birks Street and
OL,13,FCampbell Road.
OL,15,FIt was using false plates at the time
OL,16,Fand was badly damaged.
OL,18,FPolice put out an appeal at the time
OL,19,Fto help them with their enquiries.
