OL,7,FLeon's name came back and he handed
OL,8,Fhimself in at a police station three
OL,9,Fdays later, on April 14th.
OL,11,FHe was then charged with a series of
OL,12,Foffences and admitted them at an
OL,13,Fearlier court hearing, including
OL,14,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,15,Fdriving a motor vehicle dangerously,
OL,16,Ffailing to stop after a road accident,
OL,17,Ffailing to report an accident, two
OL,18,Fcounts of driving without third party
OL,19,Finsurance and two counts of driving
OL,20,Fotherwise in accordance with a licence.
