OL,7,FHe also admitted escaping from lawful
OL,8,Fcustody, two counts of assault by
OL,9,Fbeating of an emergency worker and two
OL,10,Fcounts of handling stolen goods. These
OL,11,Fwere part of separate incidents.
OL,13,FAt Stoke-on-Trent Crown Court on
OL,14,FFriday (October 3rd), Salt was jailed
OL,15,Ffor 11 years and banned from driving
OL,16,Ffor eight years.
