OL,7,FStaffordshire Police, Detective
OL,8,FConstable Tracey Gascoine said: "This
OL,9,Fwas a truly horrific incident that has
OL,10,Fleft Christopher's family absolutely
OL,11,Fdevastated.
OL,13,F"We worked hard to put the pressure on
OL,14,FSalt to come forward and confront what
OL,15,Fhe had done, despite his attempts to
OL,16,Fflee the scene of his crime.
OL,18,F"I'm pleased that we've been able to
OL,19,Fdeliver this outcome for Christopher's
OL,20,Ffamily and Salt will now face justice
OL,21,Ffor his actions."
